01:18:27.467 --> 01:18:28.737
Come here, girl. Come here.

01:19:08.877 --> 01:19:10.942
Come here, baby.

01:19:13.948 --> 01:19:17.786
<i>It hurt so much,
but I had to keep going.</i>

01:19:30.265 --> 01:19:33.401
<i>The streets and the houses
