Bella, where have you
been all this time?

01:23:52.393 --> 01:23:54.992
- Is that Bella?
- Yeah, it is. It really is.

01:23:54.994 --> 01:23:56.628
Bella!

01:23:56.630 --> 01:23:58.630
Oh, my God. It's been
like two and a half years.

01:23:58.632 --> 01:24:01.968
- Hi.
- Lucas! Olivia! Mom!

01:24:01.970 --> 01:24:03.568
I did Go Home!

